{"tid":1126650,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解出口要叫出口","createTime":"2019-04-26T13:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T09:37:16.000Z","uid":199279,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d13d52245d3e0b10f3c8fb149f93076919dc4c53","tid":1126650,"uid":199279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T13:57:12.000Z","msg":"點解出口係個口字而唔係出眼，出鼻，出耳？"},{"pid":"7cd46b0c2a6f1f87ba30169dc0394ddb52271b1a","tid":1126650,"uid":227691,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:04:20.000Z","msg":"你係咪on9<br />\n你唔問埋出火點解係火，唔係金木水土"},{"pid":"de2b5b2ecd7137faf8ef411a98e380c298a48631","tid":1126650,"uid":76038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:10:03.000Z","msg":"點解巴士要叫巴士？"},{"pid":"1335de5697c14f671ee58b7d61a51df8c4578309","tid":1126650,"uid":78336,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:10:14.000Z","msg":"其實本身叫出鼻<br />\n但係有人問 點解出鼻要叫出鼻 唔叫出口? 口仲大過鼻<br />\n於是今時今日就叫出口"},{"pid":"e4e41e6dad275421c43188f83dfe58b8122188f4","tid":1126650,"uid":244315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:40:49.000Z","msg":"點解點解要叫點解?"},{"pid":"88780b5a2a381d473e6999fe70a887added8c7a9","tid":1126650,"uid":177858,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T21:32:29.000Z","msg":"我記得之前都諗過類似野，點解狗係狗/ dog呢個字<br />\n之後去search，睇過篇文<br />\n入面講過文字本身無意思<br />\n所有都係人所賦予先有一個「意思」<br />\n當然造字法係中文字嘅源頭<br />\n但入面嘅意思都係由人去定義而且得到共識<br />\n<br />\n具體唔係好記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我都有咁諗過呢啲 都幾有趣"},{"pid":"b83acb4d6c3084355a5548557fca9ab3d49569b6","tid":1126650,"uid":182178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T21:58:53.000Z","msg":"點解platform會譯做月台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗左十幾年"},{"pid":"725aced9249a07d298392a0f1cf2a1193c6410b9","tid":1126650,"uid":199279,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b83acb4d6c3084355a5548557fca9ab3d49569b6","tid":1126650,"uid":182178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T21:58:53.000Z","msg":"點解platform會譯做月台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗左十幾年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:30:23.000Z","msg":"我都想知關月亮咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67e84e0b11da7ef90fc45d7dbf8d5ab80546f1aa","tid":1126650,"uid":4539,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b83acb4d6c3084355a5548557fca9ab3d49569b6","tid":1126650,"uid":182178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T21:58:53.000Z","msg":"點解platform會譯做月台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗左十幾年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:32:29.000Z","msg":"維基下已經有解釋<br />\n<br />\n月台，原意是「賞月的高台」。中國傳統建築中，大殿、正房前方連接台階的向前方突出的平台稱為「月台」。站在月台上，一般前無遮攔，適於賞月。古人登月台觸景生情，心情舒暢，思緒萬千，會引發出各種人生感悟，並留下眾多詩詞佳作：「明從海上來，皎皎入我牖。何如登高台，對月把尊酒」（宋敏）「夜色何蒼蒼，月明久未上。不上倚城台，無奈東南嶂。」（蘇轍）等。<br />\n<br />\n現代月台成為送迎之地，別離時的傷感，重逢時的喜悅，都匯集於此。"},{"pid":"d931edba12ed7fd389efa20c4443d2072d201d5b","tid":1126650,"uid":131262,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:11:19.000Z","msg":"點解入口叫入口？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想入口"},{"pid":"6d050304bca48041b8a26959cafdbbb1941195bd","tid":1126650,"uid":203036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cd46b0c2a6f1f87ba30169dc0394ddb52271b1a","tid":1126650,"uid":227691,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:04:20.000Z","msg":"你係咪on9<br />\n你唔問埋出火點解係火，唔係金木水土"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:33:19.000Z","msg":"女可以叫出水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c06b332e12fb65fd1e050cb643bbe8866c5bed8","tid":1126650,"uid":227691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d050304bca48041b8a26959cafdbbb1941195bd","tid":1126650,"uid":203036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cd46b0c2a6f1f87ba30169dc0394ddb52271b1a","tid":1126650,"uid":227691,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:04:20.000Z","msg":"你係咪on9<br />\n你唔問埋出火點解係火，唔係金木水土"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:33:19.000Z","msg":"女可以叫出水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T09:24:28.000Z","msg":"出火同出水意思唔一樣喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ae1f09cebb21c2e33f4b6befa56cdbbebdeeb4","tid":1126650,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T09:37:16.000Z","msg":"張碌鳩放入去既地方咪入口<br />\n相反拎出黎就係叫出口"}]}